snippet.title: The Gravity Box - Trailer
snippet.description:
Download and play The Gravity Box now!

https://henrycgs.itch.io/gravity-box

The Gravity Box is a sandbox game about gravity. But without planets.

Place objects and watch them attract to each other gracefully, create cool orbits or cause huge collisions that make loads of cubes fly away! 

This game was made by a single person. It is free, but please consider leaving a donation in order to support me!
